"org.jboss.seam.deployment.annotationTypes=com.acme.Foo:com.acme.Bar]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[# A colon-separated list of annotation types to handle\n"
"org.jboss.seam.deployment.annotationTypes=com.acme.Foo:com.acme.Bar]]>"

